      "source": "https://largohistoricalsociety.org/harbor-bluffs-on-the-waters-edge/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Dredging in the late 1950s and 1960s created “fingers” that opened many waterfront lots, boosting the subdivision’s appeal to retirees and families.",
